Electric green and orange, and could you use either the pic where they’re holding bouquets or that other image where they’re in suits with Todoroki and Ochako? Maybe spiderlillies, explosions, and sun/star themes (since they’re our twin star boys). These emojis: 🍀💥🧡💚🌟. Thank you in advance!! Your edits are so cute and pretty I love them, thank u for doing these!!
